				<h1>The Golden Road</h1>
				
				<p class="book-page-author"><a href="https://librivox.org/author/75">Lucy Maud MONTGOMERY (1874 - 1942)</a></p>
				
				<div class="description">In the sequal to <a href="http://librivox.org/the-story-girl-by-lucy-maud-montgomery/">The Story Girl</a> Sara Stanley returns to join the King children in publishing their own local magazine to entertain the town of Carlisle.<p></div>	<!-- .description -->

				<p class="book-page-genre"><span>Genre(s):</span> Children's Fiction</p>

				<p class="book-page-genre"><span>Language:</span> English</p>

				
				
